uk.co.strangeskies.expression

Class IdentityExpression<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.strangeskies.expression.ActiveExpression<T>
      • uk.co.strangeskies.expression.IdentityExpression<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the expression.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Expression<T>, Property<T>

    public class IdentityExpression<T>
extends ActiveExpression<T>
implements Property<T>
    An Expression based on the behavior of the IdentityProperty class, with the lazy updating behavior of LockingExpression for Observers.
